Output docs/demo/suggest.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 740
Set Height 480
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Set Padding 24
Set CursorBlink false

Hide
Type "export HOME=/tmp/gnbd-suggest HISTFILE=/tmp/gnbd-suggest/.zsh_history"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

Sleep 300ms
Type "gnb suggest --from-history"
Enter
Sleep 5s
